author: Edmund DeMarche
title: WHO expert warns countries easing coronavirus bans to not let guard down
description: A health expert at the World Health Organization said on Tuesday that countries that have relaxed earlier coronavirus bans due to low transmission rates should keep their guard up due to the threat of the virus surging back.
